2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the training procedures and experiments performed to study emergent languages. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with the emergence of communication in artificial agents. 
4. cs.SD (Sound) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses the emergence of language and communication. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with neural agents and their training.
